A small-town housewife, Smita is devastated to find her husband and cousin dead. What happens when the local cop, Ratan, suspects her to be the one behind their murder? Watch this cat-and-mouse chase in Saali Mohabbat, premieres 12th December 2025.

Director: Tisca Chopra 
Star Cast:
Radhika Apte
Divyendu Sharma
Anurag Kashyap
Anshumaan Pushkar
Souraseni Maitra

snippet.description:
#NessFitGamer #gta 5 #gta5hindi #gta5mods 

Franklin Opens Every HAUNTED Mystery Container In Indian Bike Driving 3D! üò±

This video is about the Indian Bike Driving 3D game, this is a horror scary story about Mystery Container or Mystery Box In Indian Bike Driving 3D. In this scary story, Franklin meets many ghosts and monsters like Granny, Siren Head, Mr. Meat, Choo Choo Charles, Zombie Michael, and Scary Teacher. To unlock his own mystery container (mystery box) in Indian Bike Driving 3D, Franklin must invite all these ghosts. Will Franklin survive this horror adventure? What is inside the mystery box of franklin of Indian Bike Driving 3D? Watch the full scary story to find out!

Kanda Sasti Kavacham is one of the most powerful devotional hymns dedicated to Lord Murugan, written by Sri Devaraya Swamigal. Listening to this divine chant helps remove obstacles, destroy negative energies, bring peace, protection, courage, and spiritual strength.
On the auspicious day of Skanda Sasti, devotees chant this Kavacham to seek the blessings of Lord Murugan and receive divine grace, victory, and positivity in life.

snippet.title: Franklin Enters Squid Game to Save Shinchan! üò≥ PART 2 | GTA 5 Malayalam
snippet.description:
Franklin & Shinchan in Squid Game Part 2 is here!üî•

In the last part, Shinchan got trapped inside the Roblox Squid Game world.
Now Franklin takes the help of Chingam Sir to find who gave Shinchan the Squid Game address.

Franklin and Chingam Sir catch the culprit at the airport, and with the information,
Franklin enters the Roblox Squid Game arena to save Shinchan.

But the Squid Game Boss refuses to release Shinchan unless he finishes the game!

Shinchan wins the Squid Game match‚Ä¶
BUT the boss cheats and plans to escape in a helicopter with all the prize money! üò°üöÅ

Franklin finds Shinchan along with Roblo, a new Roblox character, and together
they catch the Squid Game Boss and hand him over to Chingam Sir.

Album: Dude (Tamil)

Dhwani Studios

Presenting the official video of the ‚ÄúProjpati ‚Äù title track from the much-awaited film Projapati 2.
‚ÄúProjapati Song‚Äù is a high-octane Bengali wedding dance anthem packed with celebration, colour, and unstoppable energy. Composed in a Jeet-Ganguly‚Äìstyle festive dance beat.

The lyrics carry the fun, poetic, and rhythmic flavour you‚Äôd expect from a Priyo-Chattopadhyay‚Äìinspired wedding track‚Äîfull of joy, jokes, and pure celebration. Featuring the dynamic screen presence of Dev‚Äôs youthful energy and Mithun Chakraborty‚Äôs iconic swag, the track feels like a grand family celebration turned into a dance explosion.
